 *** USER WARNING MESSAGE 6173 (EQD4S)
     *** SHELL ELEMENTS WITH OFFSET GIVE WRONG RESULTS IN LINEAR BUCKLING ANALYSIS
         PROVIDED IN SOLS 5, 16, 105, 200.  RESULTS COMPUTED IN GEOMETRIC NONLINEAR
         ANALYSIS (SOLS 106, 129, 153, AND 159 WITH PARAMETER,LGDISP,1) ARE CORRECT
         IF THE SOLUTION CONVERGES.
         NOTE:
             (1) AN ALTERNATIVE IS TO REMODEL WITHOUT USING SHELLS WITH OFFSET.
             (2) The CTRIAR and CQUADR elements do support differential stiffness
                 with shell offsets.  However, the CTRIAR and CQUADR are not supported in
                 geometric nonlinear analysis.  The CTRIA3 and CQUAD4 elements can
                 automatically be converted to CTRIAR and CQUADR through SYSTEM CELL
                 (370) = 5.
